zed for its ‘zeroeffluent discharge’ status it reuses more than  per cent of process waste low carbon footprint as it recycles  of coke oven gas for power generation uses sophisticated ambient air control infrastructure beyond and has reduced gas flaring to lower levels salem worksedit jsw acquired siscol in the year  a sick unit at that time quick turnaround of the plant was achieved by expanding capacity from  mt to  mt and switching over to value added products unique features complete product range rounds  to  mm rcs  to  mm flats  to  series dsir approved rd centre with sophisticated modern equipments online automatic inspection and testing facilities for rounds and rcs up to   high precision rolling reducing and sizing block in bar and rod mill dolvi worksedit the  mtpa integrated steel plant at dolvimaharashtra majority stake acquired in  is an inherent part of jsw steel this is indians first and only operating conarc technology plant located on the west coast of india the plant has a jetty with a capacity of  million tonnes per annum this provides the unit with logistical advantages in importing raw materials and savings on freight cost the unit is connected through rail road and sea and has given the jsw steel a strategic presence in western india the dolvi plant caters to several industries including automotive projects and construction machinery lpg cylindermakers cold rollers oil and gas sector and consumer durables unique features the dolvi plant is the first in india to adopt a combination of conarc technology for steel making and compact strip production csp for producing hot rolled coils  the main feature of csp is thin slab casting it can produce coils with thickness as low as   mm hr coils produced at dolvi are feed material for the two jsw steel cold rolling and downstream facilities at vasind and tarapur vasind worksedit the vasind plant focuses on jsw branded highend steel productsit sources hr steel coils from the dolvi and vijayanagar plants to manufacture valueadded branded steel products such as galvanised steel plain and corrugated products as well as colorcoated products the journey that started in  with the commissioning of a  high cold rolling mill has turned into a fullfledged complex with cold rolling hot rolling galvanizing and colour coating facilities galvanized steel from vasind is a market leader in both domestic and international markets the unit exports mainly to the usa europe and middle east asia and south african continent the plant has a total capacity of  mtpa in galvanized and coldrolled products  mtpa color coated products and hotrolled plates manufacturing facility unique features part of india’s largest coated product producer and exporter of galvanized steel manufacturer of appliance grade color coated products a revolutionary product in the indian steel industry which will replace imported steel in the manufacture of white goods in india it has one of the plant that acquired in jsw turn around delivery time within three weeks of demand tarapur worksedit the tarapur plant marks one of the first milestones for jsw steel this plant was originally inaugurated on  may  by hon vasant rao naik the then chief minister of maharashtra the plant was acquired by late shri o p jindal on  november  from piramal steel limited and renamed jindal iron and steel company the plant offers coated products catering to several sectors tarapur plant specializes in galvanizing galvalume and color coated steels it is india’s largest producer and exporter of coated products the tarapur plant has five cold rolling mills and five coated strip divisions which include two dual pot galvanizing cum galvalume lines two color coated lines and a  mw captive power plant it has a total capacity of  mtpa including ongoing projects and sources coils from the vijayanagar and dolvi plants to manufacture valueadded branded steel products unique features the tarapur plant is specialized for the ultra thin coated products the tarapur plant features two dual product lines for galvanized cum galvalume with a coating capacity of  mtpa it also has  mw captive power plant cpp to meet the power requirement of both tarapur and vasind plant tarapur has a zero discharge facility having a multieffect evaporator system for effluent treatment it has a unique service center facility to meet the customized requirement of various segment like export oem retail for their cut sheet corrugation and profiling requirement it has also installed rainwater harvesting system to meet its water requirement kalmeshwar worksedit one of the downstream operations of jsw steel is executed from kalmeshwar the kalmeshwar plant has a pickling line two rolling mills two galvanizing lines two colorcoating lines a galvalume line six slitting and  cuttolength lines two profiling lines and a tile profiling line it was earlier ispat industries unique features zero liquid discharge facility productsedit hot rolled product cold rolled product galvanised product prepainted galvanised product electrolytic tinplate tmt bars wire rods  special steel products color coated products electrical steel competitorsedit competitors of jsw steel are tata steel essar steel and sail referencesedit  a b c httpwwwbseindiacombseplusstockreachadvancestockreachaspxscripcode  missing or empty title help cite error invalid ref tag name bseindia defined multiple times with different content see the help page  get in touch with jsw group companies jswin retrieved    jsw steel has become the second largest steel producer in the country after stateowned steel authority of india sail economictimescom retrieved    jsw group one of the fastest growing business house jswin retrieved    jsw steel ltd is one among the largest indian steel companies in india today jswin retrieved      httpwwwjswincompaniescompanyjswsteelshtml  welspun max steel sold bloomberg tv india   httpwwwjswinsteel external linksedit official website v t e steel industry of india comp